name: House Special Pho
description: slow-simmered broth, prepared with beef bones, served with rice noodles, protein (such as beef, chicken or plant-based protein) and other various toppings

name: Rare Beef Pho
description: Vietnamese soup that's made with rare beef and rice noodles such as vermicelli. It features a delicious broth, and is typically served with fresh cilantro, scallions, basil, and bean sprouts.

name: MeatBall Pho
description: Ground beef and seasonings that have been churned into a paste, and formed into round balls, similar to fish balls. Served in slow-simmered beef broth

name: Seafood Pho
description: Broth made with chicken bones and seafood, which give it a slightly sweet flavor. The ingredients include shrimp, clams, squid, onions, noodles, mushrooms, and coriander.

name: Chicken Pho
description: Lighter and clearer broth. Ingredients include ginger, fish sauce, rice noodles, shallots, green onions, and cilantro. Garnishes include lime wedges, mint, sliced chili peppers, bean sprouts, and Thai basil sprigs.

name: Vegan Pho
description: A vegan twist to the traditional pho. Broth is based on mushrooms, ginger, onions, soy sauce, cloves, cinnamon, coriander seeds, and black cardamom

name: Well Done Pho
description: A Northern Vietnamese version of phở bò (beef pho). This soup is prepared with well-done (chín) and rare or half-done beef (tái) that's cooked by the broth when served.

name: House Special Noodle Bowl
description: Grilled or barbecued meat (beef, pork, shrimp, and chicken) with 2 eggrolls on top of rice vermicelli noodle.

name: Grilled Pork Noodle Bowl
description: Grilled or barbecued pork on top of rice vermicelli noodle.

name: Grilled Shrimp Noodle Bowl
description: Grilled or barbecued shrimp on top of rice vermicelli noodle.

name: Grilled Chicken Noodle Bowl
description: Grilled or barbecued chicken on top of rice vermicelli noodle.

name: Vietnamese Egg Rolls
description: A traditional eggroll with a vietnamese spin on it.

name: Vietnamese Spring Rolls
description: shrimp and vermicelli noodle wrapped in rice paper.

name: Vietnamese meat Sandwich
description: Grilled Pork with Lemongrass inbetween bread. Ingredients include pork liver pate, vietnamese mayonnaise, pickled carrots/daiok and cilantro.

name: Dumplings
description: Consists of minced meat and finely chopped vegetables wrapped into a piece of dough skin.
